OL,3,CAn economic snapshot of Britain on the
OL,4,Ceve of war
OL,6,FThe Office for National Statistics has
OL,7,Fjust published a snapshot of the calm
OL,8,Fbefore the storm.
OL,10,FA moment in time when the UK looked
OL,11,Flike it was nearing the end of a long
OL,12,Fand wearying march back to price
OL,13,Fstability.
OL,15,FThe annual rate of inflation in the UK
OL,16,Fstood at 3% in February - with falling
OL,17,Fpetrol and diesel prices acting like
OL,18,Fgravity, pulling the headline rate
OL,19,Fdown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
