OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774515910
OL,3,CAn economic snapshot of Britain on the
OL,4,Ceve of war
OL,6,FThe war in the Gulf has changed
OL,7,Feverything.
OL,9,FSince the first missile was fired at
OL,10,FIran on February 28, the price of
OL,11,Fdiesel at the pump has risen by 31
OL,12,Fpence a litre, petrol by 16 pence and
OL,13,Fcounting.
OL,15,FOil and gas prices have spiked, and
OL,16,Fthe longer they remain at these
OL,17,Flevels, the more the price of almost
OL,18,Feverything will start to rise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
