OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774515910
OL,3,CAn economic snapshot of Britain on the
OL,4,Ceve of war
OL,6,FJet fuel, fertiliser and shipping
OL,7,Fcosts have already increased.
OL,8,FConsumers will feel the impact
OL,9,Feventually.
OL,11,FJust a month ago, the Bank of England
OL,12,Fexpected inflation to fall to within a
OL,13,Fwhisker of its 2% target in April.
OL,14,FEconomists are now rewriting their
OL,15,Fforecasts upwards.
OL,17,FThe Bank thinks inflation will hit
OL,18,F3.5% in the coming months. Capital
OL,19,FEconomics has 4.6% pencilled in before
OL,20,Fthe end of the year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
