OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774515910
OL,3,CAn economic snapshot of Britain on the
OL,4,Ceve of war
OL,6,FBusinesses may respond by raising
OL,7,Ftheir prices; workers may demand
OL,8,Fhigher pay. The concern is that
OL,9,Finflation will start to feed itself.
OL,11,F"The idea that interest rates may rise
OL,12,Fcan no longer be dismissed," says
OL,13,FSanjay Raja, Chief UK Economist at
OL,14,FDeutsche Bank.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
