OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774515910
OL,3,CAn economic snapshot of Britain on the
OL,4,Ceve of war
OL,6,FNo one expects a return to the double-
OL,7,Fdigit inflation of late 2022 - but
OL,8,Fmany households and businesses are
OL,9,Fstill feeling bruised from the last
OL,10,Fsqueeze on their living standards.
OL,12,FFood prices have settled at a level
OL,13,F32% higher than they were in February
OL,14,F2022, when Russia invaded Ukraine and
OL,15,Fenergy prices last surged.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
